The China-Eurasia Expo opens today in Urumqi, the capital of northwest China’s Xinjiang Uygur Autonomous Region. The theme is "Building the Silk Road Economic Belt Through Opening-Up and Cooperation." Full story >>
CCTV Our reporter Ming Tian is in Urumqi covering the event.
Q1: Hello, Ming Tian, what are the expectations for this year’s event?
Q2: Xinjiang has been hosting regional trade fairs for more than two decades. What is the difference between this year’s expo and ones in previous years?



